description:
My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 9

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

In Tasmania, we meet the youngest team in the competition and BBF's, Tahlia and Bianca. Can they bring enough culinary maturity to impress their fellow home chefs and judges?
